{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/vue-cli-3-x-버전에-typscript-webpack-세팅하기","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>처음에 엄청나게 삽질을 하게되는데 하고나면 또 별거아닌... 것중 하나가 웹팩세팅 아닌가 싶다. 이번에 SPA도입하면서 본격적으로 vue 빌드환경을 세팅해보게 되었는데, vue.js도 그렇지만 프론트엔드 개발환경구성 관련 기술들을 처음 접해봐서 그런지 많이 헤맸다. 해보고나니 헤맨만큼 더 잘 알것같은 느낌이 들어 좋은 경험이었다.</p>\n<h1 id=\"vue-cli-설치하기\"><a href=\"#vue-cli-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"vue cli 설치하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>vue cli 설치하기</h1>\n<p>vue cli는 2.X대랑 3.X대가 변화가 큰 편이다. 혹시 구버전이 있으면 프로젝트 생성 명령어부터 다르니 반드시 두 버전을 확인하고 개발해야한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> i -g @vue/cli</code></pre></div>\n<h1 id=\"vue-cli-프로젝트-생성하기\"><a href=\"#vue-cli-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"vue cli 프로젝트 생성하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>vue cli 프로젝트 생성하기</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">vue create <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>project-name<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>타입스크립트를 추가하고싶으면 프로젝트 생성시 설정단계를 통해 타입스크립트를 추가해도 되고, 생성된 프로젝트에 명령어로 typescript를 추가해도 된다.</p>\n<h1 id=\"생성된-vue-프로젝트에-typescript-추가하는-법\"><a href=\"#%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1%EB%90%9C-vue-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8%EC%97%90-typescript-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94-%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"생성된 vue 프로젝트에 typescript 추가하는 법 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>생성된 vue 프로젝트에 typescript 추가하는 법</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">vue <span class=\"token function\">add</span> typescript</code></pre></div>\n<p>타입스크립트 추가를 하면 <code class=\"language-text\">main.js</code>가 <code class=\"language-text\">main.ts</code>로 변경되고, 내가 설정한 옵션에 따라 이 경로에 <code class=\"language-text\">shims-tsx.d.ts</code>와 <code class=\"language-text\">shims-vue.d.ts</code>파일이 생성된다.</p>\n<h1 id=\"webpack-연동하기\"><a href=\"#webpack-%EC%97%B0%EB%8F%99%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"webpack 연동하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>webpack 연동하기</h1>\n<p>vue cli는 웹팩 위에서 빌드되는 프로젝트이므로 기본 설정만으로도 당장 테스트하기에 충분하지만 그래도 webpack에서 사용하던 설정들을 몇가지 붙여야하면 <code class=\"language-text\">vue.config.js</code>를 통해 세팅하면 된다. 최초에 기본 생성되는 파일이 아니므로 직접 만들어야한다.</p>\n<p>기본적으로 지원되는 옵션은 <a href=\"https://cli.vuejs.org/config/#global-cli-config\">공식문서</a>를 참조해서 작성하고, 나머지는 <code class=\"language-text\">configureWebpack</code>을 통해 설정한다. 해당 키값으로 설정된 옵션들은 <code class=\"language-text\">webpack</code>옵션에 <code class=\"language-text\">merge</code>되면서 빌드된다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> path          <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'path'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\tUglifyJsPlugin  <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'uglifyjs-webpack-plugin'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\trootconfig      <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'./root.config'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nmodule<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\tpublicPath<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'/'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\toutputDir<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> path<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">resolve</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>__dirname<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'./dist/'</span><span class=\"token operator\">+</span> rootconfig<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>buildpath<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\tconfigureWebpack<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\tentry<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t\tapp <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'./src/'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> rootconfig<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>buildpath <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">'main.ts'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\toutput<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t\tfilename<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'bundle.js'</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\tresolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t\talias<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"token string\">'@'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> path<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">resolve</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>__dirname<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'src/'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> rootconfig<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>buildpath<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\toptimization<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t\tminimize<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t\tminimizer<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">UglifyJsPlugin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t\t\t\tuglifyOptions<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tsourceMap<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\twarnings<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tcompress<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tunused<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tmangle<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tbeautify<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\toutput<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tcomments<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <sp